### Email Verification API Examples
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/auth
@email = test@example.com
@otp = 123456

### 1. Register User (sends OTP email automatically)
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "SecurePass123",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890"
}

### 2. Verify Email with OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "otp": "{{otp}}"
}

### 3. Resend Email OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/resend-email-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}"
}

### 4. Login (after email verification)
POST {{baseUrl}}/customer/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "identifier": "{{email}}",
  "password": "SecurePass123"
}

### 5. Get Current User (requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

